data.description: Make yourself right at home in the highly desirable city of Kyle, Tx! Also, officially known as the Pie Capital of Texas! This appealing 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home is the perfect place to be near popular surrounding cities such as Austin and San Antonio without having to live so close to the busy city life. 311 Mineral Springs includes a spacious backyard that is the perfect size for entertaining guests. During the hot months you can keep cool by heading down to the community pool! This property has so much to offer featuring a 2 1/2 car garage, epoxy garage floor, mini split, water softener, dishwasher, oven/range, large refrigerator and ring doorbell. Located nearby we find Cabela's, Buck's Backyard, Pinballz Kingdom, Sams Club, Evo Entertainment, Plum Creek Golf Course and too many to name in addition to countless eateries that'll be sure to satisfy your every craving!
